| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2348 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0c60fdfa-b536-57cb-9351-f651a0fb1e05"
